You have been asked to create a template for virtualization. The template will be in JSONformat. Which of the following is the correct name for JSON?
A)  Just Simple Object Nodes
B)  JavaScript Object Notation
C)  Java Standard Object Notation
D)  JavaScript Standard Object Notation
B
B. JSON- formatted files are JavaScript Object Notation. These files, along with YAMLfiles, are frequently used to provide templates and configuration information because bothformats are lightweight and descriptive. When working with a VM template or automation,you may encounter these formats.224Appendix  Answers to the Review Questions
